text: Aubonne was a district of the canton of Vaud in Switzerland. The capital was Aubonne. It contained the following municipalities: * Apples * Aubonne * Ballens * Berolle * Bière * Bougy-Villars * Féchy * Gimel * Longirod * Marchissy * Mollens * Montherod * Pizy * Saubraz * Saint-George * Saint-Livres * Saint-Oyens Category:Former districts of Vaud
title: Aubonne (district)
